```
.
├── equalizer.py        # Main application (all classes + entry point)
├── presets/             # Auto-generated preset JSON files
└── README.md
```

---

## 🛠️ Known Limitations

- **Mono only** — input/output is processed as a single channel for simplicity.
- **Possible feedback loop** — using speakers (instead of headphones) while monitoring live mic input can cause howling.
- **Noise reduction is basic** — `NoiseReducer` uses simple spectral subtraction; no calibration UI is currently wired into the GUI.

